{"word":"ἀναπλέκω","slug":"ἀναπλέκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναπλέκω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to enwreath</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to braid one's hair</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of writing verses, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἀναπεπλεγμένοι</el> <i>closely engaged</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}